title: Money and Sharks hit Ponce Inlet for The Arnette Cash Pot Surf Series
description:
The Arnette Cash Pot returned to the Ponce Inlet, with a few non-competitors in grey wetsuits checkout our contest. The 2 day event went off with super fun surf and local hero Aaron "Gorkin" Cormican taking the win in the pro division. Pro and groms were ripping both days and all contestants went home happy with a smile on their face because they left with some Arnette gear.

Watch our #LIVEARNETTE series videos of our riders.
